bug.short_desc: Generating markup of widgets has negative performance impact

long_desc.thetext:
The generation of the markup to show the application developer how the (generated) markup of the widget looks like is done at the startup of the website API viewer.
Since this task is time-consuming it would be a better approach to do it on demand - I guess this was intended with the "Show" / "Hide" toggle anyway.
The screenshot shows the website API viewer after startup (using Firefox on Windows). The markup is already created and highlighted.
